  "instructions": [
    "Mix flour, yeast, sugar, and salt in a bowl.",
    "Add water and knead dough for 5 minutes.",
    "Knead dough for another 5 minutes until smooth.",
    "Place dough in a greased bowl, cover, and let rise for 1 hour.",
    "Preheat the oven to 425°F (220°C).",
    "Roll out the dough to a thickness of 1/4 inch.",
    "Transfer the dough to a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Drizzle with olive oil, sprinkle with chives, and drizzle with infused oil.",
    "Bake for 15 minutes until the flatbread is golden brown.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 5 minutes.",
    "Cut into wedges and serve."
